Class ComputeWaiters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oracle.bmc.core.ComputeWaiters

public class ComputeWaiters
extends Object

    Collection of helper methods to produce Waiters for different resources of Compute.

    The default configuration used is defined by Waiters#DEFAULT_POLLING_WAITER.
